    "steam_appid": 3334510,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334510/extras/e96863ce2bcd35e3ca6adb4274edd257.avif?t=1772349784\" width=548 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在桐树街里寻找可爱的猫咪。你能找到它们吗？喵喵……猫咪在呼唤你！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334510/extras/5c8fc566f8c5110625acc4ef520b19d0.avif?t=1772349784\" width=548 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 手绘极简卡通风格</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 超过500只猫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 找到猫咪让场景拥有色彩 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 探索桐树街</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 一些有趣的互动元素</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 猫咪的叫声可以帮助你</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 拖动和缩放屏幕画面</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 放松下来 找到所有的猫</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334510/extras/ffddc61dfd271b30b732b1fc3874a11c.avif?t=1772349784\" width=548 height=180 /></span></p>",
